<Article
  title="State Farm's California Policy Drawdown 2023 to 2028 in One Chart"
  description="Timeline of State Farm's withdrawal from California homeowners insurance: the announcements, the numbers, what drove it, and what it means now."
  pillar="is-my-zip-next"
  lastUpdated="June 2026"
